# at most 1 box contains only white tennis balls
# e.g. C1W -> ¬C2W ^ ¬C3W
# In CNF:
# 1. Implication elimination: ¬C1W V (¬C2W ^ ¬C3W)
# 2. Distribute or's over and's: (¬C1W V ¬C2W) ^ (¬C1W V ¬C3W)
# 3. Break final conjunction: ¬C1W V ¬C2W, ¬C1W V ¬C3W
(or (not C1W) (not C2W))
(or (not C1W) (not C3W))
(or (not C2W) (not C1W))
(or (not C2W) (not C3W))
(or (not C3W) (not C1W))
(or (not C3W) (not C2W))

